---
title: Nan's Cheesy Beef, Pork & Bacon Lasagne with Cucumber Salad
description: Have you ever had a saucy beef ragu in a lasagne, we would love to try it out. Let’s whip one up with bacon and a Parmesan cheese mash topping. The layers of ragu will create a lasagne that everyone will be raving about.
